<para id="fs-id1171506236522">Write a few sentences about your thoughts and opinions of word problems. Are these thoughts positive, negative, or neutral? If they are negative, how might you change your way of thinking in order to do better?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1869017">
<para id="fs-id1395140">Answers will vary.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
